April 19, 1968.

No.-.

Hark, Inc., dba Pinellas General Hospital v. Cohen, Acting Secretary of Health, Education, and Welfare, et al. David Lirni and Terry A. Furnell for applicant. Solicitor General Griswold in opposition.

C. A. 5th Cir. Application

for injunctive relief presented to Mr. Justice Black, and by him referred to the Court, denied.
